I spent a lot of my 50+ time in there and it can go from Sarnak Battle Shield, sarnak bracer of honor and sarnak arcane fetish in a hour dual boxing my cleric at entry to a jade inlaid hoop from bridgekeeper and nothing else with a full group killing everything from levitation tunnel, bridge, captain to mines entry for 3 hours.<br>
