<br>
There is still the chance of getting an SBS, SoS, Sarnak Earring, and more off the non-named spawns, but most of the nicest stuff in Chardok drops of specific named mobs.  i.e. Watch Sarge, named Observer, Bridge Keeper, Grave Master, named Captain, named Foremen, and so on and so on.<br>
<br>
Nice list of named mobs and what they can drop, as well as maps here:<br>
